org.drip.calc.output

Class BondOutput

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.analytics.core.Serializer
      • org.drip.calc.output.BondOutput

  • public class BondOutput
extends Serializer
    The class implements the place holder for a comprehensive suite of analytical bond measures. Contains bid/ask sides for price, yield, G spread, Z spread, I spread, spread to treasury benchmark, par asset swap spread, work out dates, work out factors, and credit basis
